    "ts": "2026-04-29T11:29:05+00:00",
    "headline": "IDEX’s (NYSE:IEX) Q1 CY2026 Sales Beat Estimates, Stock Soars",
    "summary": "Manufacturing company IDEX (NYSE:IEX) reported Q1 CY2026 results beating Wall Street’s revenue expectations, with sales up 8.9% year on year to $886.9 million. Guidance for next quarter’s revenue was better than expected at $895.7 million at the midpoint, 0.8% above analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $2 per share was 12.9% above analysts’ consensus estimates.",
